name: ecSTATIC 3.14
description: OBJKT 2 of a 13 piece collection embodying the living-breathing life force we all bring to the Tezos blockchain by being active users of HEN. Each OBJKT in this collection is intended to abstractly relate to the collector and their personal spiritual vibrations, as well as the struggle and conflict that orbits their existence. May you find happiness wherever your thoughts wander.
